Number Format

useful NumberFormat Methods

.format() = returns a value in whichever format instance has been chained to NumberFormat.
.getCurrencyInstance() = returns a string representation of the input as a currency, e.g 12345.891 becomes $1,234,567.89.
.getPercentageInstance() = returns a string representation of the input as a percentage, e.g 0.1 becomes 10%.

